task.instruction: You are Gabrielle Cameron with the email "gabriellecameron@gmail.com", a compliance officer. You need to perform a regulatory compliance audit and performance evaluation. You want to review your user profile, examine available funds and their compliance status, analyze investor portfolios for Harris-Moody, and generate comprehensive fund valuations and profit/loss analysis for 2025-06-07. You need to ensure regulatory compliance and identify any compliance violations. You should check completed reports and NAV records for the period from 2025-05-13 to 2025-06-07. Finally, create a notification for the compliance audit with class_ "portfolios" and type "alert".
